OL,3,CSurviving member of first team to ever
OL,4,Cclimb Mt. Everest calls for crowd
OL,5,Ccontrol
OL,7,Fhas been labelled "very dirty" and
OL,8,Fovercrowded by the only surviving
OL,9,Fmember of the first mountaineering
OL,10,Fexpedition to reach its summit.
OL,12,FKanchha Sherpa, 91, said the mountain,
OL,13,Fwhich attracts thousands of tourists
OL,14,Fevery year, would benefit from a
OL,15,Freduced number of climbers.
OL,17,FHe added that people should not be
OL,18,F"dirtying" the mountain, which for
OL,19,FSherpas - a Tibetan ethnic group - is
OL,20,Fregarded as Qomolangma or goddess
OL,21,Fmother of the world.
