OL,3,CSurviving member of first team to ever
OL,4,Cclimb Mt. Everest calls for crowd
OL,5,Ccontrol
OL,7,FMount Everest's peak has been scaled
OL,8,Fthousands of times since the first
OL,9,Fconquest - which Mr Sherpa was part of
OL,10,Fin 1953 - and in the spring climbing
OL,11,Fseason of 2023 saw 667 climbers
OL,12,Fsuccessfully achieve the feat.
OL,14,FLittering concerns have grown as more
OL,15,Fpeople take on the months-long
OL,16,Fchallenge, but authorities have
OL,17,Fpreviously said they have no plans to
OL,18,Freduce the number of permits that are
OL,19,Fissued to climbers.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G2/7
