OL,3,CSurviving member of first team to ever
OL,4,Cclimb Mt. Everest calls for crowd
OL,5,Ccontrol
OL,7,FClimbers are required to bring down
OL,8,Ftheir own rubbish, equipment and
OL,9,Fanything they take with them up the
OL,10,Fmountain or risk losing their trip
OL,11,Fdeposit. However, monitoring of this
OL,12,Fhas been deemed ineffective.
OL,14,FMr Sherpa said: "It is very dirty now.
OL,15,FPeople throw tins and wrappings after
OL,16,Feating food. Who is going to pick them
OL,17,Fup now?
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.!/*%/"-$ /*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,
