PS,c000
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F312A1709605845
OL,3,CSurviving member of first team to ever
OL,4,Cclimb Mt. Everest calls for crowd
OL,5,Ccontrol
OL,7,F"Some climbers just dump their trash
OL,8,Fin the crevasse, which would be hidden
OL,9,Fat that time but eventually it will
OL,10,Fflow down to base camp as the snow
OL,11,Fmelts and carries them downward."
OL,13,FHe added: "They should not be dirtying
OL,14,Fthe mountain. It is our biggest god
OL,15,Fand they should not be dirtying the
OL,16,Fgods."
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/7
