OL,3,CSurviving member of first team to ever
OL,4,Cclimb Mt. Everest calls for crowd
OL,5,Ccontrol
OL,7,FMr Sherpa was among a 35-member team
OL,8,Fwhich helped put New Zealander Edmund
OL,9,FHillary and his Sherpa guide, Tenzing
OL,10,FNorgay, atop Mount Everest on May 29,
OL,11,F1953.
OL,13,FHe was among the three Sherpas to go
OL,14,Fto the last camp on Everest along with
OL,15,FMr Hillary and Mr Norgay.
OL,17,FThey first heard of the successful
OL,18,Fascent on the radio before being
OL,19,Freunited with the summit duo at Camp
OL,20,FTwo.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/7
