OL,3,CSurviving member of first team to ever
OL,4,Cclimb Mt. Everest calls for crowd
OL,5,Ccontrol
OL,7,F"We all gathered at Camp Two but there
OL,8,Fwas no alcohol so we celebrated with
OL,9,Ftea and snacks," he said.
OL,11,F"We then collected whatever we could
OL,12,Fand carried it to base camp."
OL,14,FThe route they opened up from the base
OL,15,Fcamp to the summit is still used by
OL,16,Fclimbers. Only the section from the
OL,17,Fbase camp to Camp One, over the
OL,18,Funstable Khumbu Icefall, changes every
OL,19,Fyear.
